summary: The retailer, situated in Tezpur, Assam, pin code 784001, branch B, wants to know the status of their complaint ID 1726712. They placed an order on July 21st but have not received it. They also state that they have not received any response to the complaint they filed. The customer support representative requests the customer's email, and informs them that they will forward the complaint to the concerned team for investigation. The retailer's email is pr_ing@gmail.com. The call gets disconnected and the retailer calls back. The customer support representative asks the retailer to provide their address and phone number. The retailer's name is NIBEDAN and the phone number is 7780774141. The call ends with the customer support representative promising to forward the complaint to the concerned team.
speaker_a_summary: The customer calls ITC and wants to know if it's possible to disconnect the line for the B area call. After checking, the customer is informed that the line can be disconnected. The customer transfers to a different language and complains about a distributor in their area. The operator takes down the necessary information to raise the complaint and asks for a reference number that the customer sent in an email to the center. The customer resends the email and provides the operator with the shop address: NIBEDAN, mercato 780 784001. The operator checks for a reference number and proceeds to connect the customer to the concern team who will check and investigate the issue. The call ends with the operator trying to contact the concern team through different numbers but with no success.
speaker_b_summary: A retailer from Tezpur, Assam, India wants to know the status of his order, which he claims he has not received. He is reaching out to the distributor, Malik, and IT Cares at itc.in. The retailer has already filed a complaint on July 21st, and is reaching out again as the status of the company is still pending. The retailer is sending a screenshot of the order to the distributor. The distributor has not yet responded to the retailer's previous communication, but they have provided a reference number for the retailer's order. The retailer is sending another email with the requested information.

- They are looking for a reference number and details on the status of their complaint. 
- The customer support representative is helpful and will forward the complaint to the concerned team. 
- The call gets disconnected and the receiver calls back.
